WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.541 --> 00:00:02.589
Inventory is the logical result

2
00:00:02.589 --> 00:00:04.421
of the action of purchasing.

3
00:00:04.421 --> 00:00:07.029
Therefore, to manage your inventory

4
00:00:07.029 --> 00:00:09.969
you need to manage your purchasing process.

5
00:00:09.969 --> 00:00:13.011
Proper levels should be set for items in the inventory

6
00:00:13.011 --> 00:00:15.923
to determine when to reorder the needed item.

